  1. Vote on how to allocate resources
  2. Demand resources
  3. Receive allocation
  4. Appropriate (take) resources
  5. Get monitored
  6. Receive sanctions if you violated rules
  7. Appeal sanctions if you think they are unfair
  8. Pool gets replenished

